  "reference_number": "RUS1387",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect Sergey Vladimirovich MIKHAILOV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following ground: Sergey Vladimirovich MIKHAILOV has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business as a Government of Russia affiliated entity, through his former role as Director General of the TASS news agency, a Government of Russia-affiliated entity. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023. \n",
